en.title: Filipino Golf Champion Angelo Que With FusionExcel
en.content:
FE is proud to announce that Angelo Que is now part of the FE international team. Angelo is the Philippines top golfer, and winner of the 2008 Philippine Open.

Angelo is highly impressed with the benefits and power of FE's Scalar Energy range of products.

Angelo Que bags Philippine Open title (Asia Golf Online.com - 6th April 2008)
